{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-js","path":"/academy/blog/posts/cryptocurrency-trading-for-beginners-on-deriv/","result":{"data":{"directus":{"blog":[{"id":"e5615ea7-a1be-4306-9725-cf576846aaf9","blog_title":"Cryptocurrency trading for beginners on Deriv","meta_title":"Cryptocurrency trading for beginners on Deriv","meta_description":"A quick guide on cryptocurrency trading for beginners. Find out what crypto pairs, trade types, and platforms are available for crypto trading on Deriv.","og_title":"A beginner's guide to cryptocurrency trading","og_description":"A quick guide on cryptocurrency trading for beginners. Find out what crypto pairs, trade types, and platforms are available for crypto trading on Deriv.","published_date":"2021-08-25","read_time_in_minutes":2,"blog_post":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trading cryptocurrency is like trading other financial markets &ndash; forex, stocks and stock indices, or commodities. All you have to do is predict the price movements of crypto assets. You gain profit when your speculations are correct.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before you dive in, it&rsquo;s crucial to have a clear understanding of the basics, such as </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/academy/blog/posts/what-is-cryptocurrency\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">what cryptocurrency is</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and how it works &ndash; just like with other markets. Once you are confident in your knowledge, you can move on to learning about cryptocurrency trading.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How to trade crypto pairs?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trading cryptocurrency pairs is very similar to trading fiat currency pairs on forex. Let's see how it works, taking the BTC/USD pair (Bitcoin against the US dollar) as an example.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you predict that the value of Bitcoin will rise against the US dollar, you can open a buy trade and get a payout if your prediction turns out to be correct. Similarly, you can go for a sell trade if you think that the value of Bitcoin will fall.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here is how it works in a nutshell:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cms.deriv.cloud/assets/67596176-f2c1-4ee8-a70f-defe689c0a7d\" alt=\"How Does Cryptocurrency Trading Work\" width=\"647\" height=\"231\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On Deriv, you can trade cryptocurrencies by going long and going short with </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/academy/blog/posts/what-is-cfd-trading/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">CFDs</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/academy/blog/posts/deriv-multipliers-how-they-work/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">multipliers</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and profit from the price movements of assets without buying or owning the actual digital coin.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How to trade cryptocurrency with CFDs on Deriv</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deriv offers 2 CFD trading platforms with cryptocurrency trading: </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/dmt5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deriv MT5 (DMT5)</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/derivx/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deriv X</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. DMT5 is our version of the world&rsquo;s most popular CFD trading platform, while Deriv X is our newest addition with a highly customisable interface. Both platforms are great for CFD trading, and the choice would purely depend on a personal preference.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are the cryptocurrencies you can trade with CFDs on both platforms:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"https://cms.deriv.cloud/assets/e88d6b70-fd0e-4830-a1c5-88b2ff21404f\" alt=\"Cryptocurrencies Available for Cfd Trading on Deriv\" width=\"647\" height=\"230\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most of them are traded against USD, while Bitcoin is also traded against Ethereum, Litecoin, Silver, and Gold.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To start trading cryptocurrency on Deriv, you will need to create a Financial account, select your preferred pair, set up the required trading parameters, and place your trade. If you need a little more guidance on setting the trading parameters for your trade on DMT5 or Deriv X, check out our step-by-step instructions.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How to trade cryptocurrency with multipliers on Deriv</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To trade cryptocurrency with multipliers, you can choose between the 3 platforms: </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/dtrader/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DTrader</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/dbot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DBot</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and our mobile app &ndash; Deriv GO. DTrader is an intuitive and user-friendly platform to use, while DBot can help you automate your strategy with a trading robot.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are the cryptocurrencies available to trade with multipliers on all 3 platforms, both traded against USD:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"https://cms.deriv.cloud/assets/c30c9f2a-d499-4751-a77c-15f67da041d2\" alt=\"Cryptocurrencies Available for Trading with Multipliers on Deriv\" width=\"906\" height=\"230\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Placing a trade with multipliers is quite simple. All you need to do is select your stake, select the multiplier and place your trade. You can also apply risk management tools, such as take profit and stop loss, to manage your trades even better.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ready to try trading cryptocurrency? Choose the platform you like the most and create a</span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/signup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> risk-free demo account</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> loaded with 10,000 USD virtual money to practise your skills!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Disclaimer:</span></em></p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Deriv GO and Deriv X platforms are not available for clients residing within the EU.</span></em></p>","author":{"id":"0d7772f6-5338-488f-a8aa-adfb6c5074b9","name":"The Deriv team","image":{"id":"9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91","description":"Deriv Logo","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/de3a1/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.png","srcSet":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/f2a56/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.png 38w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/7458e/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.png 75w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/de3a1/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.png 150w","sizes":"(min-width: 150px) 150px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/0852d/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.webp 38w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/18188/9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91.webp 75w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/c65bc/9826d676-35